I WANTED YOU TO GO TO PRISON.

04:23.013 --> 04:24.890
AND NOW I'M TOTALLY CLEAN

04:23.013 --> 04:24.890
AND SOBER,

04:24.932 --> 04:26.391
I HAVE A GOOD JOB, A GOOD LIFE,

04:26.433 --> 04:27.517
