YOU -- YOU DELIVER THESE?

04:42.407 --> 04:44.034
YEAH, YEAH.

04:42.407 --> 04:44.034
I-I DRIVE 'EM ACROSS THE BORDER.

04:44.076 --> 04:45.326
AND I DELIVER THEM

04:45.368 --> 04:47.579
TO THESE DIFFERENT WAREHOUSES

04:45.368 --> 04:47.579
ACROSS AMERICA.

