IS THIS?

36:43.451 --> 36:45.120
WHO IN THE HELL ARE YOU?

36:45.162 --> 36:46.621
ANY TROUBLE GETTING

36:45.162 --> 36:46.621
HURLEY'S CAR? NO?

36:46.663 --> 36:47.789
No, Hardison's on it.

36:47.831 --> 36:49.791
OKAY,

36:47.831 --> 36:49.791
CAN YOU GET ME ANOTHER ONE?

36:49.833 --> 36:51.877
AN IDENTICAL GOLD SEDAN.

36:51.918 --> 36:54.546
WE'RE LOOKING FOR A GOLD SEDAN.

36:54.587 --> 36:56.381
YOU JUST DESCRIBED

36:54.587 --> 36:56.381
FIVE CARS I HAVE BACK THERE.

36:57.966 --> 36:59.634
YOU BET.

37:02.679 --> 37:05.807
CUTE LITTLE TRICK YOU DID

37:02.679 --> 37:05.807
WITH THE MADONNAS.

37:05.849 --> 37:08.518
YOU CALLED US.

37:05.849 --> 37:08.518
YOU WANT TO DEAL?

37:08.560 --> 37:11.855
FOUND SOMETHING OF YOURS.

37:11.897 --> 37:13.356
OH, GOD, DON'T HURT ME.

37:13.398 --> 37:15.233
-GET OUT OF THE CAR.

37:13.398 --> 37:15.233
-[ Straining ] I'M SORRY.

37:15.274 --> 37:16.735
I'M SORRY.

37:16.776 --> 37:17.903
THE COURIER.

37:20.405 --> 37:23.533
LOOK -- YOU CAN TAKE THE CAR.

37:20.405 --> 37:23.533
SIGN OF GOOD FAITH.

37:23.575 --> 37:25.368
WE'LL TAKE COMMISSION.

37:25.410 --> 37:27.453
WE GET A TASTE

37:25.410 --> 37:27.453
OF EVERY SHIPMENT,

37:27.495 --> 37:29.330
AND YOU GUYS GET PROTECTION.

37:29.372 --> 37:31.833
FROM THE COPS AND THE IRISH.

37:31.875 --> 37:32.876
AND WHAT ABOUT HIM?

37:32.918 --> 37:34.002
OH, WE'LL DEAL WITH HIM FOR YOU.

37:34.044 --> 37:36.254
[ GROANS ]

37:39.257 --> 37:40.550
THIS A SETUP?

37:40.592 --> 37:44.221
HELL NO, MAN.

37:40.592 --> 37:44.221
I'M A DIRTY COP.

37:44.262 --> 37:48.183
LOOK -- THEY GOT CAMERAS

37:44.262 --> 37:48.183
ON EACH OF THE ENTRANCES.

37:48.225 --> 37:52.020
NOW, GIVE US TWO MINUTES

37:48.225 --> 37:52.020
TO GET OUT CLEAN, ALL RIGHT?

37:56.482 --> 38:00.528
-ELIOT AND HARDISON ALL SET?

37:56.482 --> 38:00.528
-EVERYTHING'S GOOD.

38:00.570 --> 38:01.905
SHOWTIME.

38:03.448 --> 38:04.824
[ HURLEY STAMMERS ]

38:04.866 --> 38:06.325
I-I CAN'T DO THIS.

38:06.367 --> 38:09.204
HURLEY, HURLEY, YOU AGREED.

38:09.246 --> 38:10.830
-NO, THEY'RE GONNA KILL ME!

38:09.246 --> 38:10.830
-YOU AGREED, HURLEY.

38:10.872 --> 38:12.331
NO! I CAN'T!

38:10.872 --> 38:12.331
I'M SORRY!

38:12.373 --> 38:13.917
STICK TO THE PLAN, HURLEY!

38:13.959 --> 38:16.253
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER,

38:13.959 --> 38:16.253
TIRES SCREECH ]

38:16.294 --> 38:17.921
GET THE DRUGS!

38:17.963 --> 38:22.383
YEAH, THE COURIER'S PULLED A

38:17.963 --> 38:22.383
RUNNER! HE'S HEADING YOUR WAY!

38:22.425 --> 38:25.344
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

38:31.977 --> 38:34.980
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

38:40.652 --> 38:42.279
GO! HE'S COMING

38:40.652 --> 38:42.279
AROUND TOWARDS YOU!

38:42.320 --> 38:45.115
NO, NO! STRAIGHT!

38:42.320 --> 38:45.115
NO, NO, NO, LEFT, LEFT!

38:55.667 --> 38:58.503
THERE HE IS!

38:55.667 --> 38:58.503
THE ONE WITH THE MEXICAN PLATES!

38:59.587 --> 39:02.007
FINE.

38:59.587 --> 39:02.007
WE'LL DO THIS OLD-SCHOOL.

39:04.843 --> 39:07.637
-TAKE IT EASY!

39:04.843 --> 39:07.637
-KEEP YOUR HANDS TO YOURSELF!

39:09.097 --> 39:13.310
I DON'T THINK

39:09.097 --> 39:13.310
HE'S A PRIEST, EITHER.

39:13.351 --> 39:16.146
I WANT YOU TO GET THEM OUT

39:13.351 --> 39:16.146
OF HERE, ALL RIGHT? ALL RIGHT.

39:16.188 --> 39:18.857
-I'M A RESPECTABLE BUSINESSMAN!

39:16.188 --> 39:18.857
-NO, YOU AREN'T!

39:23.111 --> 39:24.737
THE BARBERSHOP -- WITH ME,

39:23.111 --> 39:24.737
RIGHT? -- TOLD HIM TO

39:23.111 --> 39:24.737
GET A JHERI CURL

39:24.779 --> 39:26.156
'CAUSE HE DIDN'T KNOW

39:24.779 --> 39:26.156
WHAT ONE WAS --

39:26.198 --> 39:27.448
TOLD HIM IT'D MAKE HIS HAIR

39:26.198 --> 39:27.448
REAL STRAIGHT AND PRETTY.

39:27.490 --> 39:28.658
BOY LOOKED LIKE HE WAS BEAT

39:28.700 --> 39:30.243
WITH A BOTTLE OF BABY OIL

39:28.700 --> 39:30.243
FOR ABOUT A MONTH.

39:30.285 --> 39:32.578
[ LAUGHTER ]

39:32.620 --> 39:34.914
HURLEY, HOW YOU DOING?

39:34.956 --> 39:38.417
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU HAD TO BAIL

39:34.956 --> 39:38.417
ME OUT OF TROUBLE AGAIN.

39:38.459 --> 39:39.502
NO, NO, LISTEN, HURLEY --

39:39.544 --> 39:41.004
YOU PUT YOUR LIFE

39:39.544 --> 39:41.004
ON THE LINE TONIGHT

39:41.046 --> 39:42.297
BECAUSE IT WAS

39:41.046 --> 39:42.297
THE RIGHT THING TO DO.

39:42.339 --> 39:43.340
YOU REALIZE THAT, RIGHT?

39:43.381 --> 39:44.841
AND BY THE WAY, FOR THE RECORD,

39:44.883 --> 39:46.676
YOU'RE NOT THE SAME GUY

39:44.883 --> 39:46.676
YOU USED TO BE.

39:46.718 --> 39:48.345
OKAY?

39:48.386 --> 39:51.848
WELL, I KNOW I'M NOT

39:48.386 --> 39:51.848
YOUR  FRIEND, NATE,

39:51.890 --> 39:55.560
BUT FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,

39:51.890 --> 39:55.560
YOU'RE MINE.

39:55.601 --> 39:57.229
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:57.270 --> 40:00.232
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:00.273 --> 40:03.193
SHE'S NOT A NUN, IS SHE?

40:04.569 --> 40:06.029
[ SIGHS ]

40:06.071 --> 40:09.991
YEAH.

40:11.284 --> 40:12.869
OH, I'M SO SORRY.

40:12.911 --> 40:14.704
OH. NO, THAT'S OKAY.

40:12.911 --> 40:14.704
IT WAS MY FAULT.

40:14.746 --> 40:16.539
HURLEY.

40:16.581 --> 40:19.209
OH, HI. PEGGY.

40:19.251 --> 40:21.711
UM, ARE YOU GOING OUT ALONE?

40:19.251 --> 40:21.711
IT'S KIND OF LATE.

40:21.753 --> 40:23.629
YEAH, I'LL -- I'LL BE FINE.

40:23.671 --> 40:25.382
LET ME WALK YOU.

40:25.423 --> 40:29.010
UH, OKAY.

40:25.423 --> 40:29.010
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:29.052 --> 40:32.013
WHAT A GENTLEMAN.

40:29.052 --> 40:32.013
OOH! YOUR ARM. [ LAUGHS ]

40:32.055 --> 40:33.348
DO YOU LIKE TACOS AT ALL?

40:33.390 --> 40:34.682
YES.

40:33.390 --> 40:34.682
DO YOU LIKE CATS?

40:34.724 --> 40:36.351
-OH, DO I LIKE CATS?

40:34.724 --> 40:36.351
-YOU DO?

40:36.393 --> 40:40.355
OH. HEY, HEY. CAN I JUST ASK YOU

40:36.393 --> 40:40.355
ONE THING HERE BECAUSE...

40:40.397 --> 40:43.858
HOW IN THE HELL

40:40.397 --> 40:43.858
WOULD YOU GIVE HURLEY

40:43.900 --> 40:46.027
INFORMATION ABOUT

40:43.900 --> 40:46.027
HOW TO FIND ME -- EVER?

40:46.069 --> 40:49.197
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:46.069 --> 40:49.197
YOU KNOW, NATE, IT SEEMS LIKE

40:49.239 --> 40:51.532
LATELY YOU'VE BEEN SO FOCUSED

40:49.239 --> 40:51.532
ON THE PART OF THE JOB

40:51.574 --> 40:53.743
WHERE WE WRECK PEOPLE,

40:51.574 --> 40:53.743
I THOUGHT IT MIGHT BE NICE

40:53.785 --> 40:55.995
TO SHOW YOU WE ACTUALLY DO

40:53.785 --> 40:55.995
SOME GOOD IN THE WORLD.

40:56.037 --> 40:57.496
I KNOW YOU'RE MAD, BUT --

40:57.538 --> 40:59.498
HARDISON...

40:59.540 --> 41:01.876
THANKS.

41:01.918 --> 41:03.753
ALL RIGHT.

41:11.469 --> 41:14.597
YOU, UH...WE'RE GONNA...

41:14.639 --> 41:17.183
OH, YEAH, NO, HEY.

41:17.225 --> 41:19.227
OKAY.

41:21.104 --> 41:22.563
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

41:22.605 --> 41:24.732
YOU WANT TO SEE

41:22.605 --> 41:24.732
HOW MY NIGHT WAS?

41:24.774 --> 41:26.567
DON'T TALK TO THEM.

41:24.774 --> 41:26.567
THEN THEY'LL MAKE US STAY.

41:26.609 --> 41:27.568
YOU SEE THIS? YEAH.

41:27.610 --> 41:29.737
HEY, OH!

41:27.610 --> 41:29.737
THERE THEY ARE.

41:29.779 --> 41:30.905
AH.

41:30.947 --> 41:32.407
SOPHIE, THIS IS LUPE.

41:32.449 --> 41:33.950
[ ALL TALKING ]

41:33.992 --> 41:35.243
LET ME POUR YOU A DRINK!

41:35.285 --> 41:37.162
ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.

41:35.285 --> 41:37.162
WE WERE DRINKING TEQUILA.

41:37.203 --> 41:40.039
I GOT WHISKEY.
